                        >ιθ᾿</num><lb/>
                    <expan><abbr>ἰνδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></expan>
                    <num value="3">γ᾿</num> ἔτους <num value="524">φκδ᾿</num><lb/> ὁ Κύριος τῆς
                    δόξης<lb/> αὐτὸν ἀναπαύσ<supplied reason="omitted">ε</supplied>ι. Ἀμήν.<lb/></p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>+ (Here) was laid in Christ, resting among the saints, thrice-blessed Arenius
                    (son) of Abraamios, monk and priest, on the 19th of the month of Audynaius, in
                    the 3rd indiction-year, in the year 524. The Lord of Glory will grant him rest.
                    Amen.</p>
            </div>
